_sText:
This is my first map any suggestions and tips are appreciated.
There are two teleports on the map try and find them :D

If there are any problems send me a message.

*Features*
Fixed the boxes
32 spawn points
more grenades 
two teleports
4 secret healing pads look for a relevant sign to find it
Hidden smoke grenade


Extract the content of the ZIP file directly into your "cstrike" folder.

".../steam/steamapps/username/counter-strike source/cstrike"


Thanks


Jeremy.
